We are a contracting service specializing in the installation of home comfort, entertainment and technology. Whether you are fitting your new home or retrofitting your old home, or if you simply want advice on how to achieve your dream setup, we can help.

We work with licensed electricians and trades people and will make any referrals required to complete your dream setup.

Independent and Local

We are local and we hire local, meaning that if we succeed, a part of the community succeeds. We give clients and employees a name, not a number. We provide client tailored solutions. Every clientâ€™s needs are different and we want you to access our services on your terms.
